.DS_Store
*.Rproj.user

# Quarto / Shinylive build outputs (regenerate with `quarto render`)
/.quarto/
index.html
index_files/

# Pre-rendered Slim inputs for an alternate dashboard_data pipeline
/dashboard_data/

# Stray copied service worker sometimes dropped at repo root during preview
/shinylive-sw.js

# Pixi-managed environments (heavy; reproduce from pixi.toml + pixi.lock)
/.pixi/
pixi.lock

# R user-library extras installed at runtime by `pixi run setup-shinylive`
# (e.g. shinylive from CRAN; their on-disk files live inside .pixi/envs/)
